1
00:00:14,976 --> 00:00:16,394
I must be crazy.

2
00:00:16,394 --> 00:00:17,520
Why?

3
00:00:21,107 --> 00:00:22,067
You..

4
00:00:23,443 --> 00:00:25,028
Call my name.

5
00:00:30,033 --> 00:00:31,451
Ji-eun..

6
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:37,457
Unnie, just do what you want to do.

7
00:00:51,096 --> 00:00:52,013
Unnie..

8
00:00:57,519 --> 00:00:58,979
You must've been tired.

9
00:00:58,979 --> 00:01:00,563
You slept for an hour.

10
00:01:01,481 --> 00:01:02,649
An hour?

11
00:01:10,865 --> 00:01:12,200
Ah..

12
00:01:13,243 --> 00:01:14,452
Sorry.

13
00:01:14,703 --> 00:01:16,454
I should go now.

14
00:01:18,456 --> 00:01:20,375
I have to work tomorrow.

15
00:01:20,583 --> 00:01:21,876
Wait, unnie.

16
00:01:26,423 --> 00:01:29,300
What did you dream about?

17
00:01:31,261 --> 00:01:32,178
Dream?

18
00:01:33,430 --> 00:01:36,266
You called my name in your sleep.

19
00:01:39,686 --> 00:01:40,812
Huh?

20
00:01:41,187 --> 00:01:43,148
I don't remember.

21
00:01:47,027 --> 00:01:48,236
See you tomorrow.

22
00:01:59,664 --> 00:02:02,375
You're crazy, Kim So-hee.

23
00:02:28,735 --> 00:02:30,403
Did you get home safe?

24
00:02:36,534 --> 00:02:39,412
Sorry for leaving so suddenly.

25
00:02:40,038 --> 00:02:41,414
It's okay.

26
00:02:50,632 --> 00:02:53,510
Come hang out again next time.

27
00:03:05,522 --> 00:03:08,108
Unnie, just do what you want to do.

28
00:03:30,463 --> 00:03:31,172
Hey.

29
00:03:33,216 --> 00:03:34,092
Yeah?

30
00:03:35,426 --> 00:03:36,678
Are you sick?

31
00:03:38,763 --> 00:03:39,806
No.

32
00:03:41,975 --> 00:03:44,060
You've been spacing out all morning.

33
00:03:44,060 --> 00:03:45,979
You haven't eaten a single bite.

34
00:03:46,604 --> 00:03:48,439
I am eating.

35
00:03:50,024 --> 00:03:52,527
You're just stirring your soup.

36
00:03:59,534 --> 00:04:00,618
Da-yeon.

37
00:04:01,286 --> 00:04:01,995
Yeah.

38
00:04:03,705 --> 00:04:05,415
When someone..

39
00:04:05,415 --> 00:04:07,167
appears in your dream, what does it mean?

40
00:04:08,168 --> 00:04:09,502
Whose dream?

41
00:04:10,628 --> 00:04:12,213
Just in general.

42
00:04:14,841 --> 00:04:16,342
In general?

43
00:04:16,718 --> 00:04:18,219
That you miss them,

44
00:04:18,219 --> 00:04:20,013
or that you like them.

45
00:04:20,013 --> 00:04:21,514
Something like that?

46
00:04:22,932 --> 00:04:23,600
Why?

47
00:04:23,892 --> 00:04:25,351
You dreamed of someone.

48
00:04:27,145 --> 00:04:29,022
I didn't dream of anyone.

49
00:04:31,232 --> 00:04:32,358
Is it a guy?

50
00:04:33,943 --> 00:04:35,111
No.

51
00:04:38,281 --> 00:04:40,366
The thing you said you had to tell me,

52
00:04:40,366 --> 00:04:41,659
is this it?

53
00:04:42,994 --> 00:04:45,747
I told you I'd tell you later.

54
00:04:46,039 --> 00:04:48,333
Ah, why? Tell me now.

55
00:04:56,674 --> 00:04:58,134
Working late again today?

56
00:05:05,266 --> 00:05:05,934
Yeah.

57
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,353
I'll wait for you.

58
00:05:22,075 --> 00:05:23,451
Hello.

59
00:05:26,996 --> 00:05:27,914
Hi.

60
00:05:38,508 --> 00:05:40,885
Not buying Chips Ahoy today?

61
00:05:41,970 --> 00:05:42,720
Yeah.

62
00:05:43,388 --> 00:05:44,806
I don't have an appetite.

63
00:05:53,564 --> 00:05:54,399
Unnie.

64
00:05:55,942 --> 00:05:56,567
Yeah?

65
00:05:58,069 --> 00:06:00,530
Why did you just leave yesterday?

66
00:06:04,158 --> 00:06:05,618
I told you.

67
00:06:05,618 --> 00:06:09,122
I had work and was tired.

68
00:06:11,791 --> 00:06:12,667
Okay.

69
00:06:14,335 --> 00:06:15,503
Today, I!

70
00:06:16,421 --> 00:06:18,381
Finish work at 12.

71
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:20,925
Huh?

72
00:06:22,927 --> 00:06:24,637
Aren't you going to wait for me today?

73
00:06:29,642 --> 00:06:31,477
I wasn't planning to.

74
00:06:33,813 --> 00:06:35,648
Wait for me today.

75
00:06:36,983 --> 00:06:39,110
Don't run away like yesterday.

76
00:07:01,424 --> 00:07:03,176
I thought you weren't waiting.

77
00:07:05,053 --> 00:07:07,430
I'm leaving soon.

78
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:11,517
Then why are you here?

79
00:07:13,728 --> 00:07:16,022
I still have some left.

80
00:07:21,736 --> 00:07:22,528
Unnie.

81
00:07:22,528 --> 00:07:23,237
Um..

82
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:26,157
I was really tired yesterday,

83
00:07:26,157 --> 00:07:28,576
and left because I had work. Really.

84
00:07:29,327 --> 00:07:32,705
Being an office worker is really tough.

85
00:07:33,664 --> 00:07:35,917
That's not what I was going to ask.

86
00:07:38,044 --> 00:07:38,920
Huh?

87
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:41,547
Just

88
00:07:42,048 --> 00:07:45,259
was gonna ask if you were cold.

89
00:07:47,345 --> 00:07:48,429
Ah.

90
00:07:50,139 --> 00:07:52,308
It's.. a bit chilly.

91
00:07:58,439 --> 00:07:59,732
By the way..

92
00:08:01,109 --> 00:08:03,611
You called my name in your sleep.

93
00:08:04,946 --> 00:08:06,239
I sleep talk.

94
00:08:06,239 --> 00:08:08,991
I'm a really bad sleep talker.

95
00:08:11,244 --> 00:08:14,455
And my name comes up?

96
00:08:19,627 --> 00:08:21,754
What did you dream about?

97
00:08:23,548 --> 00:08:24,799
I don't know.

98
00:08:25,258 --> 00:08:27,343
I really don't remember.

99
00:08:31,264 --> 00:08:32,056
Ah! Well..

100
00:08:32,056 --> 00:08:33,766
Yesterday, half-asleep,

101
00:08:33,766 --> 00:08:36,227
I heard some kind of music?

102
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,687
Ah..

103
00:08:38,146 --> 00:08:41,065
I really love collecting songs.

104
00:08:41,607 --> 00:08:42,900
My playlist.

105
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:49,532
But recommending them

106
00:08:49,532 --> 00:08:51,534
or playing them for anyone, I've never done.

107
00:08:54,412 --> 00:08:55,621
Why?

108
00:08:56,289 --> 00:08:57,206
Just.

109
00:08:57,748 --> 00:08:59,876
I prefer listening to them alone.

110
00:09:02,753 --> 00:09:06,090
Then why to me?

111
00:09:08,259 --> 00:09:09,802
I was curious.

112
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:12,472
About what?

113
00:09:14,807 --> 00:09:16,684
The things I like..

114
00:09:17,351 --> 00:09:19,270
if unnie would like them too.

115
00:09:25,610 --> 00:09:28,446
I have a really picky ear.

116
00:09:29,780 --> 00:09:31,407
I figured.

117
00:09:31,657 --> 00:09:34,619
So I picked my absolute favorite.

118
00:10:10,821 --> 00:10:12,532
It's good.

119
00:10:17,912 --> 00:10:19,163
The song.

120
00:10:26,254 --> 00:10:27,255
Unnie.

121
00:10:27,755 --> 00:10:28,548
Yeah?

122
00:10:28,923 --> 00:10:30,299
My playlist..

123
00:10:30,841 --> 00:10:32,593
has 250 songs.

124
00:10:34,554 --> 00:10:35,388
Huh?

125
00:10:37,265 --> 00:10:39,850
I'll play you one song every day from now on.

126
00:10:40,393 --> 00:10:41,435
Then

127
00:10:41,686 --> 00:10:43,354
That's 250 days.

128
00:10:46,274 --> 00:10:49,485
We can just listen to them all in one day.

129
00:10:50,278 --> 00:10:51,445
No.

130
00:10:51,862 --> 00:10:53,990
You have to listen to one song a day.

131
00:10:56,075 --> 00:10:57,118
Why?

132
00:11:00,454 --> 00:11:02,123
If we listen to one song a day,

133
00:11:02,665 --> 00:11:04,417
we can see each other every day.

134
00:11:06,836 --> 00:11:08,421
Today too..

135
00:11:09,088 --> 00:11:10,339
Tomorrow too..

136
00:11:11,507 --> 00:11:13,009
And the day after.

137
00:11:23,936 --> 00:11:25,229
You'll catch a cold.

138
00:11:25,938 --> 00:11:27,106
Your nose is red right now.

139
00:11:28,107 --> 00:11:28,858
I'm fine.

140
00:11:28,858 --> 00:11:30,776
Let's just finish the song and go.

141
00:11:31,319 --> 00:11:33,321
No, let's go inside.

142
00:11:33,654 --> 00:11:35,656
My place is right in front of us.

143
00:11:38,451 --> 00:11:39,493
I'm going home soon..

144
00:11:39,493 --> 00:11:41,203
Just warm up before you go.

145
00:11:42,455 --> 00:11:44,165
And finish listening to the song.

146
00:11:46,083 --> 00:11:46,959
Yeah?

147
00:12:09,815 --> 00:12:11,609
I'll make some hot tea.

148
00:12:12,193 --> 00:12:13,110
Okay.

149
00:12:16,697 --> 00:12:17,782
Huh?

150
00:12:22,536 --> 00:12:24,455
[The day Terra unnie first smiled]

151
00:12:25,164 --> 00:12:27,875
The day Terra unnie first smiled?

152
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:29,752
Don't look at that.

153
00:12:36,092 --> 00:12:38,969
The day with carbo sauce on her nose.

154
00:12:42,431 --> 00:12:43,808
Is this me?

155
00:12:45,309 --> 00:12:47,019
Unnie, seriously..

156
00:12:54,068 --> 00:12:56,654
Wait, these are all about me.

157
00:12:58,447 --> 00:12:59,907
How many are there?

158
00:13:02,535 --> 00:13:04,995
One for every day.

159
00:13:17,425 --> 00:13:19,927
[Fell asleep on my shoulder. Loved her breathing]

160
00:13:23,222 --> 00:13:24,974
This one is from yesterday.

161
00:13:28,561 --> 00:13:30,813
You said I slept for an hour.

162
00:13:30,813 --> 00:13:32,565
You should've just woken me up.

163
00:13:34,692 --> 00:13:37,111
I was going to, but

164
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:40,239
I wanted to stay a bit longer.

165
00:13:41,407 --> 00:13:42,616
Together..

166
00:13:52,626 --> 00:13:54,837
You're really weird.

167
00:13:59,133 --> 00:14:02,219
I know I'm weird.

168
00:14:04,430 --> 00:14:06,640
You can't just do things like this.

169
00:14:06,891 --> 00:14:08,642
It confuses me.

170
00:14:13,439 --> 00:14:15,733
Actually, saying I'm confused

171
00:14:15,733 --> 00:14:17,318
is just an excuse.

172
00:14:21,655 --> 00:14:23,449
Honestly,

173
00:14:23,449 --> 00:14:25,284
after I get off work

174
00:14:25,284 --> 00:14:26,243
I'm so tired

175
00:14:26,243 --> 00:14:28,621
I just want to go home and crash.

176
00:14:29,246 --> 00:14:32,041
But I can't just walk past the store.

177
00:14:33,209 --> 00:14:35,961
I hover around with nothing to buy.

178
00:14:40,966 --> 00:14:42,301
Look at today.

179
00:14:42,927 --> 00:14:44,887
Why would I wait for you?

180
00:14:45,596 --> 00:14:48,182
But you told me to wait,

181
00:14:48,933 --> 00:14:50,434
so I just stayed.

182
00:14:56,190 --> 00:14:59,235
I don't know what I'm doing at my age.

183
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:03,155
I must be crazy.

184
00:15:04,907 --> 00:15:06,742
You're not crazy.

185
00:15:10,454 --> 00:15:11,664
You just..

186
00:15:12,665 --> 00:15:15,084
waited because you wanted to see me.

187
00:15:21,423 --> 00:15:22,591
Yesterday..

188
00:15:23,092 --> 00:15:25,427
when you called my name in your sleep,

189
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:28,848
I know it wasn't just sleep talking.

190
00:15:34,353 --> 00:15:36,856
Don't run away today.

191
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,156
You're right.

192
00:15:47,908 --> 00:15:49,618
It wasn't sleep talking.

193
00:15:51,203 --> 00:15:53,622
I think I like you.

194
00:15:53,873 --> 00:15:54,832
No.

195
00:15:56,917 --> 00:15:58,168
I like you.

196
00:16:00,838 --> 00:16:02,673
I like you too.

197
00:16:21,191 --> 00:16:22,026
Look at her.

198
00:16:22,026 --> 00:16:23,068
You startled me!

199
00:16:24,111 --> 00:16:25,404
Why?

200
00:16:25,821 --> 00:16:27,907
You're grinning again.

201
00:16:28,616 --> 00:16:30,326
I am not.

202
00:16:31,076 --> 00:16:32,828
You're lying.

203
00:16:33,078 --> 00:16:34,371
Hey, tell me right now.

204
00:16:34,371 --> 00:16:35,289
Who is it?

205
00:16:35,623 --> 00:16:37,207
I said it's nothing.

206
00:16:37,583 --> 00:16:38,375
Huh?

207
00:16:38,375 --> 00:16:39,418
You're really going to be like this?

208
00:16:39,710 --> 00:16:40,920
The thing you said you had to tell me,

209
00:16:40,920 --> 00:16:42,129
you still haven't told me.

210
00:16:42,129 --> 00:16:43,297
Tell me right now.

211
00:16:49,595 --> 00:16:50,638
I

212
00:16:51,221 --> 00:16:52,222
Yeah.

213
00:16:53,641 --> 00:16:55,601
Started seeing someone.

214
00:16:57,144 --> 00:16:58,520
Crazy, really?

215
00:16:58,687 --> 00:17:00,147
Crazy, seriously?

216
00:17:01,106 --> 00:17:02,524
Wow. Hey, who is it?

217
00:17:02,524 --> 00:17:03,943
Let me see a picture. Handsome?

218
00:17:05,152 --> 00:17:06,487
Uh..

219
00:17:07,947 --> 00:17:08,822
She's pretty.

220
00:17:09,990 --> 00:17:10,741
Pretty?

221
00:17:12,076 --> 00:17:14,536
You must be into pretty boy styles.

222
00:17:15,204 --> 00:17:16,080
No.

223
00:17:17,790 --> 00:17:18,707
It's a girl.

224
00:17:20,042 --> 00:17:20,626
Huh?

225
00:17:21,752 --> 00:17:23,921
The part-timer at the store by my place.

226
00:17:26,632 --> 00:17:28,509
Hey, hey, hey.

227
00:17:28,509 --> 00:17:30,052
Why are you telling me this just now?

228
00:17:30,344 --> 00:17:32,846
Ah, I thought you wouldn't believe me.

229
00:17:32,972 --> 00:17:33,931
Hey, is she pretty? Got a picture?

230
00:17:33,931 --> 00:17:34,932
How old is she?

231
00:17:35,182 --> 00:17:36,767
Be quiet, we're at work.

232
00:17:37,476 --> 00:17:38,644
Sorry, sorry.

233
00:17:39,937 --> 00:17:41,397
Ah, no wonder.

234
00:17:41,397 --> 00:17:42,398
Lately, even when you worked late,

235
00:17:42,398 --> 00:17:43,816
you never got annoyed once.

236
00:17:47,277 --> 00:17:48,195
You happy?

237
00:17:50,072 --> 00:17:50,781
Yeah.

238
00:17:51,198 --> 00:17:51,949
I'm happy.

239
00:17:54,535 --> 00:17:55,869
After work today,

240
00:17:55,869 --> 00:17:57,621
I'm going straight to the store

241
00:17:57,621 --> 00:17:58,998
and check her out myself.

242
00:17:59,123 --> 00:17:59,915
Hey.

243
00:17:59,915 --> 00:18:01,583
Don't overdo it.

244
00:18:01,583 --> 00:18:02,793
Seriously, don't come.

245
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:04,253
That's up to me.

246
00:18:04,253 --> 00:18:05,546
See you later.

247
00:18:19,727 --> 00:18:21,437
[When do you get off work?]
